mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Hot Line-Late News", "As I See It", "New Dancers Special", "Meet Mike", "History of the U.S.A. in Dance", "Take a Good Look-Couples Scoot Back", "The Dancers Walkthru", "Square Dance Diary", "Roundancer Module", "Paging the Round Dancers: Art and Ruth Youwer", "Caller's Textbook-Chapter Thirty-seven", "CALLERLAB Quarterly Movements", "Style Lab-The Thar Family", "National Convention", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Caller of the Month: Dale Casseday", "On the Record: Review", "Square Dance Date Book", and "Fashion Feature".
